comment:
* Collation element modifier. Interface class for a modifier
     * that changes a tailoring builder's temporary CEs to final CEs.
     * Called for every non-special CE32 and every expansion CE.

methods.name: long modifyCE32(int ce32)
methods.comment: Returns a new CE to replace the non-special input CE32, or else Collation.NO_CE.

methods.name: long modifyCE(long ce)
methods.comment: Returns a new CE to replace the input CE, or else Collation.NO_CE.
